org.fcrepo.server.management

Class MockManagementDelegate

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.fcrepo.server.management.MockManagementDelegate
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Management, ManagementDelegate

    public class MockManagementDelegate
extends Object
implements ManagementDelegate
    A generic management delegate for use in Journal unit testing. Each method call generates a MockManagementDelegate.Call object which is added to a list of calls for later inspection. The method then returns some plausible result value if required.
